column5: So no more dealing with windy conditions while fishing !
So no more dealing with windy conditions while fishing !  Going to keep a lt on the toon from now on. LOL
I must try that on G Bay sometime when the NW wind is up and I want to fish from my canoe!!
I listened very carefully, just in case I get on Jeopardy some day. How much oil will it take to make 1 meter waves on Erie fishable?  Exon Valdez?
Thanks, this should give me a few more fishable days on Lake O this summer
Buddy said it himself, and I'd have to agree... "Very INTERESTING, but yet, useless information.
